  <summary date="2005-07-13T17:51:35Z" status="Introduced in House">Condemns bigotry, violence, and intolerance against any religious group, including persons of Islamic faith.

Declares that the civil rights and liberties of all individuals should be protected.

Recognizes that the Quran should be treated with dignity and respect.

Calls upon local, state, and federal authorities to work to prevent bias-motivated crimes and acts against all individuals.</summary>
